# Halyvernoxian App UI Design Guidelines

## Color Scheme
```dart
// App theme colors
final darkBlue = Color(0xFF0A1931);
final deepPurple = Color(0xFF4A235A);
final accentPurple = Color(0xFF6C3483);
final lightPurple = Color(0xFF9B59B6);
final darkBg = Color(0xFF050A14);
```

## UI Components

### Cards
Cards should have:
- Rounded corners (20px radius)
- Semi-transparent background (dark blue with opacity)
- Subtle border with purple tint
- Soft shadow effect
- Backdrop filter blur for glass effect

### Buttons
Primary buttons should have:
- Linear gradient background (deepPurple to accentPurple)
- 16px border radius
- Icon + text layout
- Hover effect with slight elevation
- Padding: 14px 24px

### Navigation
Bottom navigation bar should have:
- 4 items: Love Diary, Luggage, Generator, Profile
- Icon + text for each item
- Active state with purple highlight
- Semi-transparent background with blur effect

### Status Bar
Status bar should have:
- Semi-transparent dark background
- App name in center
- Time on left
- Status icons on right

### Progress Indicators
- Linear progress bars with gradient fill
- 4px height, rounded corners

### Text Styling
- Font: System font (no custom fonts)
- Headings: Bold weight, 24px for section titles
- Gradient text effect for important numbers/statistics

### Special Effects
- Pulse animation for important elements
- Subtle transitions between screens
- Micro-interactions for buttons and toggles

## Screen-Specific Guidelines

### Love Diary Screen
- Prominent day counter with gradient text
- Timeline with vertical line and dot indicators
- Memory cards with image previews

### Luggage Screen
- Trip cards with countdown badges
- Checklist with clear checked/unchecked states
- Progress bar for packing completion

### Cartoon Generator Screen
- Large preview area for generated images
- Text input with suggestion chips
- Grid layout for history items

### Profile Screen
- Circular profile area at top
- Settings toggles with custom switch design
- Statistics in card layout
